      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "一颗小球从高处滑到低处，走哪条路最快？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "直觉会说：两点之间直线最短，那自然最快。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "可是最短并不等于最快，这正是三百年前的著名谜题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "problem",
      "line_id": "prob-1",
      "filename": "problem-prob-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/problem-prob-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "一六九六年，伯努利向全欧洲数学家公开征解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "problem",
      "line_id": "prob-2",
      "filename": "problem-prob-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/problem-prob-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "据说牛顿收到问题，当晚就给出了答案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "problem",
      "line_id": "prob-3",
      "filename": "problem-prob-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/problem-prob-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "这道题催生了一门全新的数学分支——变分法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "energy",
      "line_id": "en-1",
      "filename": "energy-en-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/energy-en-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "由能量守恒，小球的速度只取决于它下落的高度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "energy",
      "line_id": "en-2",
      "filename": "energy-en-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/energy-en-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22464,
      "text": "一开始陡一点，就能更快获得速度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "energy",
      "line_id": "en-3",
      "filename": "energy-en-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/energy-en-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "于是走一条先陡后缓的曲线，反而比直线更快到达。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "cycloid",
      "line_id": "cyc-1",
      "filename": "cycloid-cyc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/cycloid-cyc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "这条最快的曲线，正是滚动圆上一点画出的摆线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "cycloid",
      "line_id": "cyc-2",
      "filename": "cycloid-cyc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/cycloid-cyc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "看画面里三颗球同时出发，摆线上的球总是最先到底。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "cycloid",
      "line_id": "cyc-3",
      "filename": "cycloid-cyc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/cycloid-cyc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "它还是等时曲线：从任意点释放，到底部用时都相同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brachistochrone",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brachistochrone/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
